    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Psychic power runs thorough your blood, whether it be from a familial predisposition to psychic power or exposure to a powerful psychic phenomenon. Whatever the source of this power, your mind is a dangerous weapon.</em></p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Class Skill:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/sense-motive\">Sense Motive</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.rvf2gxyy1d4strae]{Mind Thrust I}&nbsp;(3rd),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.fa3oswb6t4drz74g]{Id Insinuation I}&nbsp;(5th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.z6xg1ckozmmx2s3q]{Ego Whip I}&nbsp;(7th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.twthnjx7cnvfzez2]{Intellect Fortress I}&nbsp;(9th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.199pl2cgawz38smh]{Psychic Crush I}&nbsp;(11th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.uid5nvg542oquom3]{Mental Barrier V}&nbsp;(13th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.fe4zq5n7gewou9mg]{Tower Of Iron Will III}&nbsp;(15th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.v39qnirlhgje2c0e]{Bilocation}&nbsp;(17th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.esugpfcs3zwbujt1]{Microcosm}&nbsp;(19th).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bonus Feats:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/metamagic-feats/focused-spell-metamagic\">Focused Spell</a>,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.O109YFcItBFUDHvu]{Heighten Spell},&nbsp;</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/metamagic-feats/intuitive-spell-metamagic\">Intuitive Spell</a>,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.iAbIGhm7T2OK9Brt]{Iron Will},&nbsp;</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/metamagic-feats/logical-spell-metamagic\">Logical Spell</a>,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.L10V7jTzmMYz62zz]{Persuasive},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.wFoLrh5FeeqBXsQ8]{Quicken Spell},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/sense-motive\">Sense Motive</a>),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.V2zY7BltkpSXwejy]{Spell Focus}.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Arcana:</strong> Your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;spells and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Spell-Like-Abilities-Sp-\">spell-like abilities</a>&nbsp;count as psychic instead of arcane. You use thought and emotion&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Components\">components</a>&nbsp;instead of verbal and somatic&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Components\">components</a>&nbsp;when casting your spells.</p>\n</div>",
